ActDepartment of Veterans Affairs Act
SubjectOrder offering a social support to Canadian Armed Forces members and veterans who experienced sexual misconduct during their service, and to their family members
PrecisOrder assigning to the Minister of Veterans Affairs the power to develop, establish and implement social support programming by way of peer support to Canadian Armed Forces members and veterans who experienced sexual misconduct during their service, and to their family members, that contributes to the well-being of those members and veterans and their families.
